high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the bin
pick up a grinder from the shelf
move to the stove to the right of the sink
put the grinder in the cabinet farthest from the stove
move to the counter behind you
pick up a grinder from the counter
move to the stove to the right of the sink
put the grinder in the cabinet farthest from the stove on the right
anns.task_desc: Pit two grinders in the cabinet farthest from the stove on the right.

high_descs: Turn right and then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Pick up the pepper shaker on the left of the microwave.
Turn around and walk over to the stove and face it.
Open the cupboard on the far right and put the pepper shaker inside and close the door.
Turn around and then turn left and face the table with the stool.
Pick up the pepper shaker from the table.
Turn around and go back to the cupboard.
Open the cupboard on the far right and put the pepper shaker inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put the two pepper shakers away.

high_descs: Walk to the pepper grinder to the left of the microwave on the shelf.
Pick up the pepper grinder from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the cabinets to the right of the oven.
Place the pepper grinder in the rightmost cabinet next to the oven.
Turn around and walk to the pepper grinder on the counter with lettuce on it.
Pick up the pepper grinder on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the cabinets to the right of the oven.
Place the pepper grinder in the rightmost cabinet next to the oven.
anns.task_desc: Place two pepper grinders in the rightmost cabinet next to the oven.
